description: What’s going on this weekend? Just set your home city, and then you can ask what’s going on tonight, this weekend, or on a specific date. You can also ask what’s happening in another city. It’s your direct access to StubHub – just by asking Alexa.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask StubHub what’s happening this weekend.
Alexa, ask StubHub what’s going on tonight.
Alexa, ask StubHub what’s happening in San Francisco.
name: StubHub
shortDescription: What's going on this weekend? Ask Alexa to find out from StubHub!
